Q: aplicatie formular cu campuri pentru nume si email, pentru job se alege dintr-un combobox
A:
layout = QFormLayout()
layout.addRow(QLabel("Formular job"))
layout.addRow("Nume:", QLineEdit())
layout.addRow("Email:", QLineEdit())
cb = QComboBox()
cb.addItem("Avocat")
cb.addItem("Doctor")
cb.addItem("Programator")
layout.addRow("Job:", cb)
self.btn_trimite = QPushButton()
layout.addWidget(self.btn_trimite)
self.btn_trimite.clicked.connect(self.close)
self.setLayout(layout)
Q: aplicatie care calculeaza varsta, se introduc datele personale (nume, prenume, data nasterii si studiile din combobox) si un buton care calculeaza varsta
A:
layout = QFormLayout()
layout.addRow(QLabel("Cel mai performant calculator de varsta"))
layout.addRow("Nume:", QLineEdit())
layout.addRow("Prenume:", QLineEdit())
layout.addRow("Data nasterii:", QDateEdit())
cb = QComboBox()
cb.addItem("Scoala")
cb.addItem("Liceu")
cb.addItem("Facultate")
layout.addRow("Studii:", cb)
self.btn_calculeaza = QPushButton("Calculeaza varsta")
layout.addWidget(self.btn_calculeaza)
self.btn_calculeaza.clicked.connect(self.close)
self.setLayout(layout)
Q: un formular pentru rezervare camera de hotel, se cer nume, tipul camerei din combobox, data rezervarii si durata sejurului din spinbox
A:
layout = QFormLayout()
layout.addRow(QLabel("Rezerva camera pe care o doresti!"))
layout.addRow("Nume:", QLineEdit())
cb = QComboBox()
cb.addItem("Single")
cb.addItem("Dubla")
cb.addItem("Apartament")
layout.addRow("Camera:", cb)
layout.addRow("Data rezervarii:", QDateEdit())
layout.addRow("Durata sejurului:", QSpinBox())
self.btn_rezerva = QPushButton("Rezerva camera acum!")
layout.addWidget(self.btn_rezerva)
self.btn_rezerva.clicked.connect(self.close)
self.setLayout(layout)
Q: aplicatie pentru rezervarea biletului de tren, se cer nume, cnp, clasa din combobox, data calatoriei si destinatia
A:
layout = QFormLayout()
layout.addRow(QLabel("Rezervarea biletului de tren"))
layout.addRow("Nume:", QLineEdit())
layout.addRow("CNP:", QLineEdit())
cb = QComboBox()
cb.addItem("Clasa I")
cb.addItem("Clasa II")
layout.addRow("Clasa:", cb)
layout.addRow("Data calatoriei:", QDateEdit())
layout.addRow("Destinatie:", QLineEdit())
self.btn_rezerva = QPushButton("Confirma rezervarea")
layout.addWidget(self.btn_rezerva)
self.btn_rezerva.clicked.connect(self.close)
self.setLayout(layout)